{"id": "1414800363818713099", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "其实忘却篇就是不怎么吃启灵的", "timestamp": "2025-09-09T02:31:32.454000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414800411696566323", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是最后发现，还是拆分机制更赚钱", "timestamp": "2025-09-09T02:31:43.869000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414800494593048647", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "星辰篇的每个角色基本上都是非常平滑的，越抽越强", "timestamp": "2025-09-09T02:32:03.633000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414828834594885724", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 19, "author_id": "1403431686116741143", "author_name": "2300011747", "author_bot": false, "content": "星辰篇就是感觉特别割裂一点都不平滑啊。比如说熔朵得超限才能玩的舒服。杜勒加强之前也得三启才厉害。忘却篇常驻角色倒是做的还不错，但是有些限定角色也不太行，比如羊妈得2启，血希得3启。拆分机制对于一个卡牌类游戏还是太过分了一点个人认为，希望游戏后面还是要改一下这个问题。（BTW皮克曼零启基本是完全体了可以参照一下这个设计）", "timestamp": "2025-09-09T04:24:40.416000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["845527584157597716"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1414800363818713099", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414829331925962764", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "我说的平滑实际上指的是，抽完部分启灵以后，一直往后抽一直有提升", "timestamp": "2025-09-09T04:26:38.989000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-09T04:28:17.074000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414829402671550557", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是忘却篇很多角色实际上，抽到关键启以后就没什么提升了", "timestamp": "2025-09-09T04:26:55.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414829462385852549", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "就像羊抽到2启3启，和+12是基本上没区别的", "timestamp": "2025-09-09T04:27:10.093000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
